snippet.title: Body And Soul game trailer
snippet.description:
LT: Mūsų pirmas žaidimas „Body And Soul“ pagaliau išleistas! Jį galite rasti per Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.comp.gamy  (arba Google Play paieškoje įrašydami Molten Neon)
----------------------------------
EN: Our first game "Body And Soul" is officially out! You can find it on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.comp.gamy  (or by typing Molten Neon in Google Play)
